<!DOCTYPE html>
<!--[if (IE 8)&!(IEMobile)]><html class="no-js lt-ie9" lang="en"><![endif]-->
<!--[if (gte IE 9)| IEMobile |!(IE)]><!--><html class="no-js" lang="en"><!--<![endif]-->
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html" charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
    <title>{{code}} - {{message}}</title>
    <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="True">
    <meta name="MobileOptimized" content="320">
    <meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{asset "favicon.ico"}}">
    <meta http-equiv="cleartype" content="on">
    <link href="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <link href="/assets/css/screen.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" ><!-- 注意相对路径前面加 / 号 -->
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      {{navigation}}
    </header>
    <main class="container" style="padding-top: 90px;">
      <section>
        <div>
          <p>非常抱歉让您看到此页面，若地址输入无误，则这很可能是 hfun.me 自身的问题。</p>
          <p>您可以尝试通过以下方法来解决：</p>
          <ul>
            <li><b>搜索</b> 您需要的内容，站内搜索位于页面上方；</li>
            <li>在本站任意文章下方 <b>留言</b>，您将很快得到回复。</li>
          </ul>
          <p>以下信息提供给技术人员：</p>
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-warning" role="alert">
          <p><b>错误代码:</b> {{code}}; <b>报错信息:</b> {{message}}</p>
        </div><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
      </section>
      {{#if stack}}
      <section class="error-stack">
        <h3>Stack Trace</h3>
        <p><strong>{{message}}</strong></p>
        <ul class="error-stack-list">
          {{#each stack}}
            <li>
              at
              {{#if function}}<em class="error-stack-function">{{function}}</em>{{/if}}
              <span class="error-stack-file">({{at}})</span>
            </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </section>
      {{/if}}
    </main>
    {{ghost_foot}}{{! Ghost outputs important scripts and data with this tag }}
    <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="http://cdn.bootcss.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>  
  </body>
</html>